        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks HG for specimen of <hi rend="italic">Mitella</hi>.</p> 
            <p>CD has tried effects of carbonate of ammonia on chlorophyll grains, but his observations are hardly trustworthy. He finds stooping over the microscope affects his heart.</p>
